      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap runabout or a project with potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little vehicle that still has plenty to offer the right buyer. It starts, drives, and could make a great budget commuter, first car, or weekend fixer-upper for someone handy. If you want something affordable without spending a fortune, this is a solid opportunity. Priced to sell and ready for its next chapter.",
