    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with solid project-driver potential. The powertrain pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels composed enough to be a practical budget ride or a great starting point for someone who knows their way around basic maintenance. It shows cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections consistent with a lower-priced vehicle, but it remains a straightforward, honest car with usable performance and plenty of life left for the next owner willing to give it some attention. Priced to move for someone looking for inexpensive transportation with mechanical upside.",
